params.token: Reward token to claim (address(0) for ETH).

claimRewards().details: Also syncs rewardDebt to current accumulators.

params._iAERO: The iAERO token to be staked.

exit().details: Updates debts to the latest accumulators after exit.

returns.amounts: Amounts pending for each token in `tokens`.

notifyRewardAmount(address,uint256).details: If there are no stakers, rewards are queued and pushed to the accumulator on first stake.

params.token: Reward token address (use address(0) for ETH).

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions. Can only be called by the current owner. NOTE: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby disabling any functionality that is only available to the owner.

params.index: Index into the reward token list.

returns.token: Address of the reward token (address(0) for ETH).

stake(uint256).details: Harvests rewards before updating balances and debts.

params.amount: Amount of iAERO to stake (must be > 0).

stakeFor(address,uint256).details: Harvests rewards for `user` before updating balances and debts.

params.amount: Amount of iAERO to stake (must be > 0).

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.

unstake(uint256).details: Harvests rewards before decreasing balances and updating debts.

params.amount: Amount of iAERO to unstake (must be > 0 and <= staked).

PRECISION().notice: Precision used for the per-share accumulator math.

accRewardsPerShare(address).notice: Returns the accumulator for a given reward token.

claimReward(address).notice: Claim rewards for a single token.

claimRewards().notice: Claim all pending rewards across every registered reward token.

exit().notice: Exit fully: claim all rewards and unstake all iAERO.

getPendingRewards(address).notice: Computes pending rewards for an account across all reward tokens.

getRewardTokens().notice: Returns the list of reward tokens (address(0) = ETH).

iAERO().notice: The iAERO token that is staked in this contract.

notifyRewardAmount(address,uint256).notice: Notify newly available rewards. Pulls ERC20 from sender; accepts ETH via msg.value.

rewardTokens(uint256).notice: Returns the reward token at index.

rewardTokensLength().notice: Returns the number of reward tokens.

stakeFor(address,uint256).notice: Stake iAERO on behalf of another user.

totalStaked().notice: Total iAERO staked across all users.
